long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Use this extension to go to the initial commit on a GitHub page. Follow along a repository you'd like to learn the life cycle of, try imitating it for a learning project, or see what technologies they started with.
